reduce PAPR, combining LDSLM algorithm with clipping and ﬁltering (CAF) algorithm, the hybrid algorithm can weigh the performance of PAPR and BER. By choosing parameters reasonably, the PAPR is effectively reduced while the BER performance of the system is guaranteed.

