II. FBMC /OQAM SYSTEMS
A. Basic principle of FBMC/OQAM system
The transmitter structure of FBMC/OQAM is shown in Fig. 1. The input of the FBMC/OQAM system is generally a complex signal, which can be expressed as:

Xm,n = am,n + j × bm,n

(1)

where n ∈ [0, N − 1], m ∈ [0, M − 1], am,n and bm,n are the real part and the imaginary part signals on the mth subcarrier
of the nth symbol respectively.

